tip.text: Walked in for a pedicure & served by the 2nd surliest manicurist ever. Monocle is right - svc stds here suck http://mothership.sg/2014/02/no-monocle-cafe-in-spore-because-service-standards-lacking/
White Russian tasted like Kahlua and milk, no vodka. I'm not coming back. Wunderbar two doors over is much better.
